     FAB#PW8L CF  E                    WORKSTN
     F                                        RRN1  KSFILE SFL01
     FAB#PP82 UF  E           K        DISK                      A
     FAGDPL12 IF  E           K        DISK
      *-----------------------------------------------------------
     E                    CMD     1   2 78
     E                    RTE        30 10
      *-----------------------------------------------------------
     I            DS
     I                                        1 300 RTE
     I                                        1  10 A8RT01
     I                                       11  20 A8RT02
     I                                       21  30 A8RT03
     I                                       31  40 A8RT04
